{"tid":455680,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"想溝以前既下屬，有冇得唸","createTime":"2017-11-02T10:18:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T11:46:28.000Z","uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"684d0d9b2e40b4d27db3784adbb25a4ecfaa1b24","tid":455680,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T10:18:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56cadfaec7066170cb308328ed0680108fce92eb","tid":455680,"uid":7628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T10:40:43.000Z","msg":"點解唔溝肥絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8803afd84e0fa3a7c4ca629954bad10e50ca5a5b","tid":455680,"uid":7628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T10:40:44.000Z","msg":"點解唔溝肥絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7805cbf9b6f8446af4d5238a9f659f98d0975a1b","tid":455680,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T10:45:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔溝肥絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢係我隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fe57814907fc6f438e6998dc1c690179a0c7c44","tid":455680,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T11:26:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"00e66073d570210783d503c45c980fd9243f1564","tid":455680,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T11:40:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>肥絲大隻男人扮女人，鐵證如山，本癲狗發現左之後，知道原來自己係同緊一個變態人妖溝通，已懊悔不已，所以決定拆穿佢既罪行，免得各位受騙:</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>肥絲原來係肥佬扮肥婆!</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家唔知一定以為肥絲係女人啦, NO NO NO, 其實佢係男人黎, 睇下, 佢又自爆啦:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s22.postimg.org/i8z8gk3xt/Screenshot_2017-05-27-09-23-42.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs22.postimg.org%2Fi8z8gk3xt%2FScreenshot_2017-05-27-09-23-42.png&h=6a188dbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男人老狗幻想自己係女人都算啦, 但竟然幻想自已係肥矮臭柒毒既肥婆, 誤導各位, 真係又核突, 又變態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過, 補充一點, 佢肥矮臭柒毒係事實, 不過係肥矮臭柒毒既麻甩佬, 並唔係肥婆囉.<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">快D用假膠黎掩飾啦傻鳩</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ff79664a59dccf7e12512131a444251ef39352","tid":455680,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T11:43:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c3bf9966714dc723dba2d8e1ad5973191300d6af","tid":455680,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T11:46:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">當肥鳩大隻被拆穿其柒點時，就會以話自己&ldquo;假膠&rdquo;同話對方&ldquo;真心膠&rdquo;來為自己辯護，如下圖:</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s26.postimg.org/huoj9jqeh/Screenshot_2017-09-29-14-11-56.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs26.postimg.org%2Fhuoj9jqeh%2FScreenshot_2017-09-29-14-11-56.png&h=0f10322e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可惜條傻鳩唔明白一個道理，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">就係明眼人一睇就知，肥鳩其實就係故事主角既投射</span></span></strong>，例如牠本身又肥又矮，就會引用d主角又肥又矮既故事。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>所以各位都爭相留下正皮，表示對其恥笑及支持本癲狗的撚狗行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span></span>"}]}